{"tid":428770,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"能仁子曰:「能者，仁也。故曰能仁」","createTime":"2017-10-08T10:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T11:18:46.000Z","uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f32366f6c0a181ffe42086a101021fa15d31004","tid":428770,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東者，大也。故曰東大。"},{"pid":"303b2e678e17d5e67b50b52bb4ecfbd44d21b94b","tid":428770,"uid":137166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a05ae55e5aab014ff609f9f96ffb3aa2d8409911","tid":428770,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"六常問仁。能仁子曰: 「仁者多能，能人所不能。人者低能，能仁所不能。能仁形影不離，故曰能仁。人稱之能大，仍因明末倭賊見人皆稱撚大唷。撚能音類，故曰能大。」"},{"pid":"2b05cf6b78406a44e62b713858f6c1723c45d269","tid":428770,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>綠者，常也。故曰綠常<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 綠你個頭"},{"pid":"eb6f2465977fb028583d5b23447a9a5523d9a933","tid":428770,"uid":139107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"